title: DAZ3D - Jazmine HD for Victoria 7
description:
Details
Jazmine is a beautiful, dark-skinned new lady for Victoria 7.

Long hours of work went into the morphs to create a truly unique character. The skin was crafted from high-res photos, no resources were used. The textures are based on the Genesis 3 Female Base UV maps, so the skin will work with every other character. Advanced Iray and 3Delight materials are included.

What's Included and Features
Jazmine for Victoria 7 (.DUF)
Jazmine Character
Shaping Presets:
1 Custom Head Morph Apply/REM for Victoria 7
1 Custom HD Head Details Morph Apply/REM for Victoria 7
1 Custom Body Morph Apply/REM for Victoria 7
1 Custom HD Details Body Morph Apply/REM for Victoria 7
Material Options:
6 Make-Ups and 1 No Make-Up (Default) Option
6 Lip Colors and 1 Default Option
5 Eye Color Options
3 Eye Reflection Options (for 3Delight)
2 Eyelash Options
Anatomical Elements Texture
Textures Include:
33 Texture, Bump, SSS and Specular Maps (4096 x 4096)
21 Texture, Bump, SSS and Specular, Reflection and Transparency Maps (2048 x 2048)
This product uses the Genesis 3 Base Female UV Maps
Daz Studio 3Delight Material Presets (.DUF)
Daz Studio Iray Material Presets (.DUF)
